  "text": "A pharmacokinetic model principally following the one described by Lockwood [CITATION_1] was developed using the Simbiology Toolkit of MATLAB (Mathworks, United States). Simbiology provides a graphical environment and programming tools to model, simulate, and analyze PK applications. Specifically in this case, it allows for simplified development, programming and debugging, of the PK model including the numerical solver of the resulting system of differential equations.",
